Enroll a girl

Big Sister proudly accepts referrals from parents, grandparents, teachers, guidance counselors, other family members and service providers.

Get Started
content.contentBlock1:
Get Involved

There are many ways to get involved with Big Sister to help us better serve girls - and we are grateful you've chosen to learn more!

Make an Impact
content.contentBlock3:
Donate

Big Sister raises 85% of our annual operating budget through private philanthropy. Your donation ensures the lasting impact of our organization on Greater Boston's girls.

Ways to Help

content.body:
Mission

We ignite girls' passion and power to succeed through positive mentoring relationships with women and enrichment programs that support girls' healthy development.
